==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crown colony
<hw>Crown colony</hw>. <def>A colony of the British Empire not having an
elective magistracy or a parliament, but governed by a chief magistrate
(called Governor) appointed by the Crown, with executive councilors
nominated by him and not elected by the people.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crowned</ent>⟦br⟧
